{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Darin, I don't have the right to give you the visa, but the right is only given to the consul general in Paris.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am sending a special courier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If within 48 hours I don't have a visa for you, I know who is going to Australia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am leaving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am resigning my job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in 48 hours, I had the visa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm telling only about-- how it were, the conditions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- I came by boat from Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was in August, '48.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I still came to the train in Munich in my army Jeep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And all the team was there to say good bye to me, Beaufort, and all the other members of the team.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I left, I charge the boat in Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the worse boat which was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] available, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was belonged to a Greek guy who was the father-in-law of Onassis Niarchos.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Dirty [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was a boy taken by the Allies during the First World War from Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a freighter-- was a freighter before the World War.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this boat was going, it took as along as Captain Cook to come to Australia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Really, 10 weeks from Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] When we came on the boat, there was UNRRA representative, English guy, actually from Canada, highly anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he started-- they were on the boat, Jews, and Latvians, and Estonians, and what have you, all mixture of different nationalities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The condition was for all the boats and planes that they should not take more than 10% of Jews, but this was-- for example, there was going a group of children, waifs, sent by HIAS-- and officially, they were going as non-Jewish from Paris.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, to cover the 10% problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
